Experience Improved Performance for Big Objects

Show Users Recommendations with Suggested for You

Enable relevant, personalized suggestions based on your company’s specific business needs and processes. Suggested for You provides recommendations to adopt new features, ways to do more with what you have, and products we think your users can benefit from.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in all editions except Essentials.

When: This feature becomes available on July 12, 2024.

How: From Setup in Lightning Experience, in the Quick Find box, enter Adoption Assistance, and then select Adoption Assistance.
